{"tid":629173,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企人嘅個人衛生意識愈黎愈差.......","createTime":"2018-04-14T13:08:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T06:57:16.000Z","uid":36868,"like":23,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"12693c05941334152c6345e7f628b3e2043bf1ff","tid":629173,"uid":36868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T13:08:42.000Z","msg":"前幾年都唔係咁<br />\n依家去完廁所唔會洗手, 再走去煮飯.....<br />\n有時夜晚直頭唔沖廁, 我一早起身就聞到尿餲味......<br />\n就算痾屎定尿都好沖廁都唔會閂廁板.......<br />\n<br />\n係床頭整個紙兜用黎放垃圾, 乜都丟入去但係幾日都唔清<br />\n牙籤又有紙巾又有, 而且丟完入去嘅會重用<br />\n係, 你冇睇錯, 牙籤都會重用......<br />\n<br />\n用黎剪雜物嘅鉸剪剪食物<br />\n就算好油都係抹一抹就算唔會拎去洗<br />\n有時為方便唔理生定熟都用同一把剪<br />\n有次我走去洗一洗把剪佢就屌鳩我多餘<br />\n唔信咁就食得死或者會肚痛<br />\n<br />\n呀, 好辛苦<br />\n有咩方法可以令佢意識到咁係唔乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點先可以令佢改咗呢啲壞習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fda0194323684d039f74a7baa96113fdba9f5239","tid":629173,"uid":31410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T13:10:55.000Z","msg":"我屋企人同你差唔多 偏偏我有潔癖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾努力去清潔個屋企轉個頭又比佢哋整污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5722f2c934372ccbb5aa94002a454f4886d12299","tid":629173,"uid":36868,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fda0194323684d039f74a7baa96113fdba9f5239","tid":629173,"uid":31410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T13:10:55.000Z","msg":"我屋企人同你差唔多 偏偏我有潔癖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾努力去清潔個屋企轉個頭又比佢哋整污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T13:21:58.000Z","msg":"屌有時會覺得係我自己誇張咗<br />\n但係我都係你地教出黎<br />\n即係你地本身都好有衛生意識啦<br />\n因乜解究呢幾年變成咁呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45c4d711f04153dfadf620130060367f8f6f342d","tid":629173,"uid":66213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T13:29:03.000Z","msg":"最頂唔順係有時晾衫架無位用之後拎我條晾緊嘅底褲掛去個鞋櫃到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知我有無誇張，但係我覺得鞋櫃無論咩位都好污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbe429a111d24199fd8e986425122cd7c73cab70","tid":629173,"uid":145394,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T13:44:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/14/214412_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F214412_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=d3d02473&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3532d8163f234b722925faf254f1b9c893e25544","tid":629173,"uid":78349,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T13:47:45.000Z","msg":"我覺得人老左就係會咁 可能佢地啲感官認知退化左 我媽都係咁 所有野都係油淋淋 食完飯洗碗都唔洗落洗潔精 過下水就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話極都唔聽 仲要去垃圾站執人掉既傢私<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後頂唔順搬"},{"pid":"744d0338cccab22dfffb4ed474a0ed9a354b696d","tid":629173,"uid":3649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T14:55:50.000Z","msg":"我老爺有樣嘢我最頂唔順，<br />\n平時要浸食材，例如冬菇，<br />\n成日唔開多盤乾淨水黎洗，<br />\n就咁放入浸緊污糟碗嗰兜又油又肥嘅水度...<br />\n<br />\n我次次係屋企見到都一定拎返出黎，<br />\n有次食飯話佢，佢就話自己會洗得好乾淨先煮，<br />\n我嗰日講咗句：「你要洗何必又索啲污糟嘢入去？做返轉頭都有嘅？」<br />\n之後佢就冇再咁浸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  階段件勝利<br />\n<br />\n仲有佢痾尿成日滴到地下都係，<br />\n不過惟有忍下，始終佢老啦眼睇唔太清 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8358d2e1731a986e9c00fd0b3089c81893263fa","tid":629173,"uid":162332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T15:40:07.000Z","msg":"我屋企人又係，最慘係我細佬屙完屎啲屎漬又唔清走，一撻痴係到又臭，廁所板成日有尿積，連去屋企廁所都要無影櫈同每次都要用花灑沖廁所<br />\n同佢地講反而係話返我轉頭唔幫手洗廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但個問題根本就係你地去得乾淨啲，自律啲成件事就好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有用手打曱甴可以唔洗手，最多係用水沖一沖就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時真係想自己搬岀嚟住，但一諗到佢地係屋企人，都唔想佢地啲無咩衛生意識，但又唔知點改變佢地"},{"pid":"e0dc4e337dc8e649e72ffd6d8f966c81f155c3c9","tid":629173,"uid":157128,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T15:44:04.000Z","msg":"敢問各位係咪住公屋?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9101086d3b6dec59984e9d9f96d5b8de398d03c7","tid":629173,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T15:45:49.000Z","msg":"你講我？"},{"pid":"e822c396f50fdcf673764411df395c067dfcee92","tid":629173,"uid":166368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T15:47:10.000Z","msg":"永遠我執完屋 唔洗幾粒鐘就打回原形<br />\n躁了"},{"pid":"e5f60be5250f8923688c34d0184a026de62a5b32","tid":629173,"uid":60279,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T15:52:09.000Z","msg":"唔滿意咪自己住囉<br />\n要食人住人既 係咁架啦<br />\n<br />\n有D野你睇人唔幀眼 人地睇你唔順眼架姐"},{"pid":"ffed9255a16f958b500271cba80db18c602153ec","tid":629173,"uid":179723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T16:26:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我屋企人又係，最慘係我細佬屙完屎啲屎漬又唔清走，一撻痴係到又臭，廁所板成日有尿積，連去屋企廁所都要無影櫈同每次都要用花灑沖廁所<br />\n同佢地講反而係話返我轉頭唔幫手洗廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但個問題根本就係你地去得乾淨啲，自律啲成件事就好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">仲有用手打曱甴可以唔洗手，最多係用水沖一沖就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n有時真係想自己搬岀嚟住，但一諗到佢地係屋企人，都唔想佢地啲無咩衛生意識，但又唔知點改變佢地</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3b05e93cd5833b8e8cfe892f4d2842d5cdb4613","tid":629173,"uid":61398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T16:28:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"28a4dfd67f3d6a13a1099434284dd58733a67932","tid":629173,"uid":45161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T16:40:56.000Z","msg":"洗碗永遠沖沖水就算數<br />\n有跡都唔會搵個百潔布捽下佢<br />\n食完飯抹枱正常抹走d污糟嘢都會搵嘢接住佢<br />\n直接掃落地 而地下幾個月先拖一次<br />\n最撚離譜令我想搬出去嘅事<br />\n係企缸發現有屎跡 係企缸呀屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔撚明點解企缸會有屎<br />\n好彩呢樣屌咗幾次暫時冇再發生<br />\n不過已經促使要拿拿聲儲夠錢搬出去"},{"pid":"24334d1676239a27449639cc3b0b7b7fd054f72d","tid":629173,"uid":172020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T18:51:29.000Z","msg":"屋企又係⼁乛⼀⼀⼁⼁⼀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c87489fe40d36a621ecf08c6e4d18755d74903f","tid":629173,"uid":143646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T02:26:41.000Z","msg":"放棄"},{"pid":"319b77888e32e574d6af1a3833b1caeb42e2cdee","tid":629173,"uid":123605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T02:28:02.000Z","msg":"SAME<br />\n唯有自己清潔多啲<br />\n真係頂唔順咪搬囉"},{"pid":"fbfdfb4838d747217049ad2d2209ed717065beda","tid":629173,"uid":13645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T02:28:22.000Z","msg":"腦退化症"},{"pid":"f96c11c1f9c7aa9a00641000627d2f2be5a2fb90","tid":629173,"uid":54597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T02:34:27.000Z","msg":"我都係咁<br />\n日日洗野拖地周圍噴火酒<br />\n閂埋佢房門當唔知<br />\n唔坐梳化直接入房<br />\n我廁所同廚房地下好似公廁咁<br />\n成日有水又著鞋踩入去<br />\n好多黑鞋所同蒜頭衣<br />\n仲有好多迷樣小型垃圾"},{"pid":"32ac0ec7d5ef04d1c3dd9170dac7cf63665f534a","tid":629173,"uid":1580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T02:38:02.000Z","msg":"我老豆用洗完腳既水 用黎拖地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ba5dd0e23071fed14656b64ad8b9b7b3eb2334f","tid":629173,"uid":85564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T02:51:43.000Z","msg":"睇字都想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c1b68bc1335060b9d0b90eea3181b89a04e48d","tid":629173,"uid":55523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:02:08.000Z","msg":"無法想像人住既地方可以咁污糟"},{"pid":"cdc45c8c824176b6fed097fad0cd37c7e53ce9ba","tid":629173,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:08:13.000Z","msg":"買/捉幾十隻小強/老鼠掉落佢間房"},{"pid":"8cd415041a2334d97a03cacdc8defdabf08386e0","tid":629173,"uid":130950,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T06:52:45.000Z","msg":"老母喺我中學嗰時 日日用裝完生肉啲碗裝早餐<br />\n<br />\n我日日返學校搞肚痛 最後比我發現鬧左佢一餐<br />\n<br />\n都唔知係咪想謀殺我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}